

# <type>(<scope>): <subject>     # ≤72 chars, imperative mood
#
# <body — explain *why*, not *what*. Wrap at ~72 cols.>
#
# <optional footer: BREAKING CHANGE: ..., refs #N>
#
# Types:
#   feat     — user-visible new capability
#   fix      — bug fix
#   ux       — UI/copy/visual polish, no new capability
#   build    — build_app.sh, Package.swift, icon, Info.plist
#   refactor — restructure, no behavior change
#   chore    — tooling, scripts, repo housekeeping
#   docs     — README / CHANGELOG / COMMITS
#   style    — formatting only
#
# See COMMITS.md for full convention and examples.
